  Universal SAVE & STACKS (sessionStorage 'ss_stacks_v1'):
    ssToggleSave(clip, btnEl)   save (opens stack picker) / unsave
    ssIsClipSaved(id)           bool
    ssGetStacks()               all stacks
    ssCreateStack(name) / ssRenameStack(id, name)
    ssAddClipToStack / ssRemoveClipFromStack / ssRemoveClipFromAllStacks
    ssShareStack(stack)         share a stack (Web Share / clipboard)
    ssSyncAllSaveBtns()         repaint all [data-save-id] buttons
    ssOnStacksChange(fn)        live re-render subscription (Watchlist)

  Universal FOLLOWING (sessionStorage 'ss_following_v1'):
    ssGetFollowing()            followed curator records
    ssIsFollowing(username)     bool
    ssToggleFollow(curator) / ssFollow / ssUnfollow
    ssWireFollowButtons(root)   make any [data-follow] button real+synced
    ssOnFollowingChange(fn)     live re-render subscription
    Used by Feed clip, clip viewer, Discover search, public profile.
    Following anywhere shows up in Profile -> Following.

  Open a curator profile (app-wide):
    ssOpenCurator(curator)      navigate to that curator's PUBLIC profile
                                (showshak-profile.html?face=public&curator=)
    ssWireCuratorLinks(root)    make any [data-curator] element open the
                                curator on click (stops propagation so it
                                doesn't trigger the clip). Wired on EVERY
                                curator name/avatar across Feed, the clip
                                viewer, Discover (results + cards), and
