    ssResolveCuratorViewModel(usersRow, contentRows, followerCount)
                                      → { found, profile, clips, stats }
                                      (existence gate; identity fallbacks;
                                      clips via ssMapContentRowsToClips)
    ssBuildOnboardingPatch(input)     build the Become-a-Curator users
                                      update {role:'curator', username?,
                                      bio?, genres?, avatar_url?} — omits
                                      empty fields, allowlisted keys
    Used by the public-curator-profile + curator-role-persistence features
